        <ExplanationTxt>ANY REQUEST FOR GOVERNING DOCUMENTS AND FINANCIAL INFORMATION MUST BE MADE IN WRITING AND THE REQUEST WILL BE REVIEW AND ACTED PURSUANT TO BOTH FEDERAL AND CALIFORNIA STATE LAW.</ExplanationTxt>
